#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.digikam.appdata.xml:6
msgid "digiKam"
msgstr "digiKam"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.digikam.appdata.xml:7
msgid "Photo Management Program"
msgstr "Clár Bainistíochta Grianghraf"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.digikam.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"digiKam is an advanced open-source digital photo management application that "
"runs on Linux, Windows, and MacOS. The application provides a comprehensive "
"set of tools for importing, managing, editing, and sharing photos and raw "
"files. You can use digiKam’s import capabilities to easily transfer photos, "
"raw files, and videos directly from your camera and external storage devices "
"(SD cards, USB disks, etc.). The application allows you to configure import "
"settings and rules that process and organize imported items on-the-fly."
msgstr ""
"Is feidhmchlár bainistíochta grianghraf digiteach foinse oscailte chun cinn "
"é digiKam a ritheann ar Linux, Windows, agus MacOS. Soláthraíonn an "
"feidhmchlár sraith chuimsitheach uirlisí chun grianghraif agus comhaid amha "
"a allmhairiú, a bhainistiú, a chur in eagar agus a roinnt. Is féidir leat "
"cumais allmhairithe digiKam a úsáid chun grianghraif, comhaid amha agus "
"físeáin a aistriú go héasca go díreach ó do cheamara agus ó fheistí stórála "
"seachtracha (cártaí SD, dioscaí USB, srl.). Ligeann an feidhmchlár duit "
"socruithe agus rialacha allmhairithe a chumrú a phróiseálann agus a "
"eagraíonn míreanna allmhairithe ar an toirt."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.digikam.appdata.xml:16
msgid ""
"digiKam organizes photos, raw files, and videos into albums. But the "
"application also features powerful tagging tools that allow you to assign "
"tags, ratings, and labels to photos and raw files. You can then use "
"filtering functionality to quickly find items that match specific criteria."
msgstr ""
"Eagraíonn digiKam grianghraif, comhaid amha, agus físeáin in albaim. Ach tá "
"uirlisí clibeála cumhachtacha san fheidhmchlár freisin a ligeann duit "
"clibeanna, rátálacha, agus lipéid a shannadh do ghrianghraif agus do "
"chomhaid amha. Ansin is féidir leat feidhmiúlacht scagtha a úsáid chun "
"míreanna a chomhlíonann critéir shonracha a aimsiú go tapa."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.digikam.appdata.xml:21
msgid ""
"In addition to filtering functionality, digiKam features powerful searching "
"capabilities that let you search the photo library by a wide range of "
"criteria. You can search photos by tags, labels, rating, data, location, and "
"even specific EXIF, IPTC, or XMP metadata. You can also combine several "
"criteria for more advanced searches. digiKam rely on Exiv2 library and "
"ExifTool to handle metadata tag contents from files to populate the photo "
"library."
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith le feidhmiúlacht scagacháin, tá cumais chuardaigh chumhachtacha "
"ag digiKam a ligeann duit cuardach a dhéanamh ar an leabharlann grianghraf "
"de réir raon leathan critéar. Is féidir leat grianghraif a chuardach de réir "
"clibeanna, lipéid, rátála, sonraí, suímh, agus fiú meiteashonraí sonracha "
"EXIF, IPTC, nó XMP. Is féidir leat roinnt critéar a chomhcheangal freisin le "
"haghaidh cuardaigh níos airde. Braitheann digiKam ar leabharlann Exiv2 agus "
"ExifTool chun ábhar clibeanna meiteashonraí ó chomhaid a láimhseáil chun an "
"leabharlann grianghraf a líonadh."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.digikam.appdata.xml:27
msgid ""
"digiKam can handle raw files, and the application uses the excellent LibRaw "
"library for decoding raw files. The library is actively maintained and "
"regularly updated to include support for the latest camera models. digiKam "
"can also manage video files for cataloging purpose, and the application uses "
"the FFmpeg backends to extract metadata and play media."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le digiKam comhaid amha a láimhseáil, agus úsáideann an "
"feidhmchlár an leabharlann LibRaw den scoth chun comhaid amha a dhíchódú. "
"Déantar an leabharlann a chothabháil go gníomhach agus a nuashonrú go rialta "
"chun tacaíocht a thabhairt do na samhlacha ceamara is déanaí. Is féidir le "
"digiKam comhaid físe a bhainistiú freisin chun críocha catalógaithe, agus "
"úsáideann an feidhmchlár na cláir chúltaca FFmpeg chun meiteashonraí a "
"bhaint amach agus meáin a sheinm."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.digikam.appdata.xml:33
msgid ""
"The application provides a comprehensive set of editing tools. This includes "
"basic tools for adjusting colors, cropping, and sharpening as well as "
"advanced tools for, curves adjustment, panorama stitching, and much more. A "
"special tool based on Lensfun library permit to apply lens corrections "
"automatically on images. The famous Gmic-Qt plugin is also available with "
"more than 600 filters to extend your creativity. All editing operations in "
"digiKam are versioned."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an feidhmchlár sraith chuimsitheach uirlisí eagarthóireachta ar "
"fáil. Áirítear leis seo uirlisí bunúsacha chun dathanna a choigeartú, "
"bearradh agus géarú chomh maith le huirlisí chun cinn chun cuar a "
"choigeartú, fuáil lánléargais agus go leor eile. Ceadaíonn uirlis speisialta "
"bunaithe ar leabharlann Lensfun ceartúcháin lionsa a chur i bhfeidhm go "
"huathoibríoch ar íomhánna. Tá an breiseán cáiliúil Gmic-Qt ar fáil freisin "
"le níos mó ná 600 scagaire chun do chruthaitheacht a leathnú. Tá gach "
"oibríocht eagarthóireachta i digiKam leaganach."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.digikam.appdata.xml:39
msgid ""
"Extended functionality in digiKam is implemented via a set of tools based of "
"plugins mechanism (named DPlugins for digiKam Plugins). Plugins can be "
"written to import and export contents to remote web-services, add new "
"features to edit image, and batch process photo."
msgstr ""
"Cuirtear feidhmiúlacht leathnaithe i digiKam i bhfeidhm trí shraith uirlisí "
"bunaithe ar mheicníocht breiseán (ar a dtugtar DPlugins do Bhreiseáin "
"digiKam). Is féidir breiseáin a scríobh chun ábhar a allmhairiú agus a "
"onnmhairiú chuig seirbhísí gréasáin iargúlta, gnéithe nua a chur leis chun "
"íomhá a chur in eagar, agus grianghraf a phróiseáil i mbaisceanna."

